  "texts": [
    "As expected, we found that more complex prompts tend to elicit superior results with advanced versions of LLMs.",
    "We introduced LEAP, a research prototyping platform designed to harness the great opportunities of LLMs for personalized learning and interaction in educational settings.",
    "The primary objective of LEAP is to implement methods that support students by providing formative feedback during problem-solving tasks, thereby promoting the concept of self-regulated learning.",
    "Empirical ev-idence to date suggests that formative feedback, when combined with cognitively activating activities, enhances learning gains.",
    "We propose that such methodologies can be extrapolated beyond traditional classroom settings and integrated into educational platforms."
